    "name": "dismiss_toast_preserves_durable_row",
    "scenario": "A background build completes with a durable output. The lineage delivers on durable_job_row with a mirror toast on tier_transient. The user closes the toast (dismiss). The lineage records the dismissal with mutates_source_object = false and preserves_durable_history = true — the durable_job_row for the build completion stays intact in the activity center, the build artifact is not removed, and the export preview and evidence packet still resolve through the lineage's linkback records. A later acknowledge on the attention_item clears the completion_unread badge without altering the underlying canonical object.",
